#ReplicaSets ğŸ‘¥ 

A ReplicaSet helps manage trafficğŸš¦by scaling your applicationğŸ“±to have multiple instances of the same pod. This helps reduce traffic to one particular instance and also helps in load-balancing traffic between each of these instances.
